LeadParagraph: This is how high the summer movie stakes have become: “Men in Black 3,” representing the return of Will Smith after a four-year hiatus, took in about $55 million over its first three days in North American theaters — and Hollywood collectively winced.

Headline.Main: ‘Men in Black 3’ Leads Weekend Box Office
